{
  "stem": "19795.1",
  "chunk_idx": 5,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 12.0,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 90,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "No, they-- no older people, no, they didn't, no.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 90,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "But some people, they worked.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 90,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Some who had a chance worked with the-- who paid.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 90,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "They'd work for them.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 91,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Oh, yeah, for sure they pay.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 91,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "For nothing, they didn't work, and maybe.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 92,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Hm?",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 93,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "1942.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 94,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "'42.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 95,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "To one place, yes, on one side of the city.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 96,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "They used to live, yeah, usually, yeah.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 96,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "There was the ghetto, and everybody went.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 97,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Hm?",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 98,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Oh, the [NON-ENGLISH] ghetto was quite big.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 98,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "You know-- one part of the city.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 99,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "No, no.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 99,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "No, it was not fence.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 99,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "But you couldn't go there.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 99,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "It police, you know.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 99,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "It was a special place where-- how you called it?",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 99,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "There was something like a bridge, a small one.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 99,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "So nobody went, but everybody was afraid.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 100,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yes, and then it was there-- in the ghetto was the hospital.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 100,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "It was a hospital there, [PAUSES FOR 5 SECONDS] which it was the hospital was there before the war also.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 101,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yeah, not a-- not a big one, because we had-- we had hospitals, a few of them.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 101,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "But this one was a small one.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 101,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And-- [PAUSES FOR 8 SECONDS]",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 102,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "It was a few-- a few Jewish doctors that was in the town, and it was nurses Jewish and Polish, oh yeah.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 103,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "In the ghetto, yes.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 103,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "It was there.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 103,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "It was another hospital, a big one.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 103,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "But this was a small one.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 103,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "It was special, I think, for the-- for the ghetto people-- a small one.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 104,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "No.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 104,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Only from Luck.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 104,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "But when they killed, they-- I think they got some from the small villages also to into Luck, and then-- then they killed already.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 104,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "When it was the [INAUDIBLE], you know, to kill the Jews.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 105,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So what was life like in the ghetto?",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 105,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "What did you do in the ghetto?",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 105,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "In the ghetto, nothing.",
      "word_count": 4
    }
  ],
